- Traditional New Year decoration
- Two round mochi rice cakes
- Topped with a bitter orange (daidai)
- Symbol of family prosperity

---

# Otoshidama / お年玉
![center-image](assets/images/otoshidama.png)

- Money gift for children
- Given in special envelopes
- Important New Year tradition
- Symbol of good luck and prosperity

